text:
That's all the material I want you to read at this time,
so if you have any questions or concerns, just ask.

Yes...!
Can I read them here?

Of course.
Please take your time.

Oh, have you finished reading?
Is there anything you don't understand?

N-No...!
I think I understand the general content.

But, I still have no idea
how I should approach this myself...

I see... That makes sense.
If you want, I can think about it together with you...

Thank you, Producer-san...!
But... could we do that a little later?
I want to try thinking about it on my own first.
